Alhambra.East Pasadena, California:
East Pasadena is a census-designated place (CDP) in Los Angeles County, California, United States. The population was 6,144 at the 2010 census, up from 6,045 at the 2000 census.


== Geography ==
East Pasadena is located at 34°8′24″N 118°4′40″W (34.140057, -118.077650).
